# CommitCloud for Git

## Preparation

1. Create a new repo for commitcloud: `mkdir .git/cc; (cd .git/cc; git init --bare)`
2. Add hook:
  `ln -s /path/to/this/repo/bin/cc-update .git/hooks/post-commit`
3. Optional: Add `git ccgit` alias for debugging:
   `git config --global alias.ccgit "\!/path/to/this/repo/bin/cc-git"
